        <p>I keep learning. I do love translation -- no longer for high scores in school -- since it's really interesting to break the walls between the people from different backgrounds.</p>
        <p>I attempt to achieve every idea and dream. I begin to learn to play the piano. And I begin to erect this website for me.</p>
        <p>Wish a <strong>regretless</strong> life!</p>
